== Methods of power management ==

=== BIOS ===

Disable unused devices right in the [[BIOS]] or EFI firmware. Potential devices to disable include:

* Serial ports
* Parallel ports
* Ethernet network devices
* Wireless network devices
* Bluetooth controllers

